1
00:00:28,380 --> 00:00:31,760
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Detente, por favor, Ericht!</font>

2
00:00:32,390 --> 00:00:34,450
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Entonces no molestes a mamá.</font>

3
00:00:36,020 --> 00:00:38,630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Lo hace todo por mí.</font>

4
00:00:39,310 --> 00:00:41,230
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¿Por qué viniste?</font>

5
00:00:41,850 --> 00:00:43,900
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Regresa a la escuela con tus amigos.</font>

6
00:00:44,900 --> 00:00:49,700
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Es problema nuestro porque
solo podemos vivir en la tormenta.</font>

7
00:00:50,200 --> 00:00:53,290
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Tú olvídate de ello, Suletta.</font>

8
00:00:54,120 --> 00:00:55,170
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡No!</font>

9
00:00:55,530 --> 00:00:59,270
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡No puedo fingir que no sé nada!</font>

10
00:01:00,500 --> 00:01:03,630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Eres muy terca, Suletta.</font>

11
00:01:11,010 --> 00:01:12,070
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Detente, Lauda!</font>

12
00:01:12,550 --> 00:01:14,650
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¿Por qué atacas a la nave?</font>

13
00:01:15,300 --> 00:01:16,490
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¿Y tú qué?</font>

14
00:01:17,310 --> 00:01:19,980
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¿Por qué estás con esa chica?</font>

15
00:01:20,390 --> 00:01:21,330
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¿Lauda?</font>

16
00:01:22,350 --> 00:01:25,170
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Si Miorine no hubiera
involucrado a los Gundams,</font>

17
00:01:26,110 --> 00:01:27,150
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">ahora Petra…</font>

18
00:01:34,070 --> 00:01:36,370
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¿Por qué nos ataca Lauda?</font>

19
00:01:36,530 --> 00:01:37,730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Ni idea!</font>

20
00:01:39,540 --> 00:01:40,910
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Felsi!</font>

21
00:01:41,660 --> 00:01:43,080
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Nos alcanzará.</font>

22
00:01:43,250 --> 00:01:44,920
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">-Nika. Chuchu.
<i>-Recibido.</i></font>

23
00:01:45,380 --> 00:01:47,480
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Vamos, Demi Barding!</font>

24
00:01:54,550 --> 00:01:56,470
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">La zona de la tormenta</font>

25
00:01:56,640 --> 00:01:58,820
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">anulará las comunicaciones Permet.</font>

26
00:01:58,970 --> 00:02:01,020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Cambien a las ópticas inalámbricas.</font>

27
00:02:01,180 --> 00:02:04,550
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Bien. Cortando enlace Permet
del Demi Barding.</font>

28
00:02:15,820 --> 00:02:19,190
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Moriremos!</font>

29
00:02:19,410 --> 00:02:20,970
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Mamá!</font>

30
00:02:24,460 --> 00:02:25,870
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Lo siento, chicos.</font>

31
00:02:26,330 --> 00:02:30,690
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">No sabía que era tan difícil
pilotear sin Permet.</font>

32
00:02:35,010 --> 00:02:37,850
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¿Esto es la tormenta de datos?</font>

33
00:02:38,890 --> 00:02:41,660
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Es una sensación desagradable, ¿verdad?</font>

34
00:02:41,810 --> 00:02:44,130
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Vayan a Quiet Zero cuanto antes.</font>

35
00:02:44,350 --> 00:02:46,450
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡A mí no me des órdenes!</font>

36
00:02:48,900 --> 00:02:52,030
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><font size="24"><font size="18">Episodio 23













<font size="30">Bondad innegociable</font></font></font></font></b></font>

37
00:04:30,330 --> 00:04:31,130
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Detente!</font>

38
00:04:31,290 --> 00:04:34,770
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">El Schwarzette…
¡El Gundam te absorbe la vida!</font>

39
00:04:34,920 --> 00:04:38,010
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">En ese caso, mátame para detenerme.</font>

40
00:04:38,170 --> 00:04:39,570
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Como a papá.</font>

41
00:04:41,590 --> 00:04:42,850
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Contéstame!</font>

42
00:04:43,850 --> 00:04:46,030
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¿Por qué no me dijiste lo de papá?</font>

43
00:04:46,850 --> 00:04:48,730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¿Te sentías culpable?</font>

44
00:04:49,310 --> 00:04:51,950
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¿O es que creíste
que no podría con ello?</font>

45
00:04:56,820 --> 00:04:59,700
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¿Tan poco me valoras?</font>

46
00:04:59,860 --> 00:05:00,970
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡No!</font>

47
00:05:01,450 --> 00:05:03,150
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Lo de papá es mi pecado.</font>

48
00:05:03,570 --> 00:05:06,010
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Debo cargar con ello yo!</font>

49
00:05:07,160 --> 00:05:09,910
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Eso es lo malo, hermano.</font>

50
00:05:12,620 --> 00:05:16,950
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Por eso Miorine se aprovecha de ti
y tú te aferras a ella!</font>

51
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:24,090
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Tu nobleza y tu arrogancia.</font>

52
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:26,630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Esos son tus pecados!</font>

53
00:05:35,270 --> 00:05:37,030
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Se acerca una nave pequeña.</font>

54
00:05:37,400 --> 00:05:39,920
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Código de identificación
de Benerit Group.</font>

55
00:05:40,320 --> 00:05:42,010
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Nos envía una transmisión.</font>

56
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:43,450
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¿Una sola?</font>

57
00:05:43,740 --> 00:05:44,750
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Conéctala.</font>

58
00:05:46,370 --> 00:05:49,430
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Guston Parche, inspector de la Unión.</i></font>

59
00:05:49,700 --> 00:05:51,390
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Quiero hablar con la central.</i></font>

60
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:54,290
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Esto no es asunto suyo, inspector.</font>

61
00:05:55,420 --> 00:05:58,710
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Se respeta el sistema
de control empresarial.</i></font>

62
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:03,510
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¿Delling Rembran?</font>

63
00:06:04,300 --> 00:06:07,390
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Mi empresa solicita
una reunión de emergencia</font>

64
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:11,470
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">en base al Acta de la Unión.</font>

65
00:06:11,930 --> 00:06:13,520
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>¿Una reunión de emergencia?</i></font>

66
00:06:14,310 --> 00:06:16,870
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Una con los representantes afiliados</font>

67
00:06:17,190 --> 00:06:21,490
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>para deliberar de nuevo
sobre la intervención actual.</i></font>

68
00:06:26,030 --> 00:06:27,220
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Presidente.</font>

69
00:06:27,370 --> 00:06:29,690
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Gracias por su colaboración.</font>

70
00:06:39,670 --> 00:06:41,340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Vete, Suletta.</font>

71
00:06:41,840 --> 00:06:44,530
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">No quiero lastimarte.</font>

72
00:06:47,760 --> 00:06:50,230
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Yo tampoco!</font>

73
00:06:50,970 --> 00:06:52,700
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Pues no nos detengas.</font>

74
00:06:52,850 --> 00:06:54,930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Es lo que desea mamá.</font>

75
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:57,390
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Crear un lugar para Eri.</font>

76
00:06:58,770 --> 00:07:01,670
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¿Y para ello engullirán varios frentes?</font>

77
00:07:02,940 --> 00:07:04,190
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¿Arrebatarán vidas?</font>

78
00:07:04,610 --> 00:07:06,810
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Eri nunca haría eso.</font>

79
00:07:07,700 --> 00:07:09,740
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Pero si te interpones,</font>

80
00:07:10,120 --> 00:07:12,070
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">mamá no dudará.</font>

81
00:07:12,450 --> 00:07:14,460
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Por eso quiero detenerlas.</font>

82
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:18,910
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">No dejaré que mamá
se vuelva una bruja malvada.</font>

83
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:30,780
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Por favor, Suletta,
olvídate de nosotras.</font>

84
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:34,680
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡No!</font>

85
00:07:37,190 --> 00:07:39,810
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Te quiero, Ericht!</font>

86
00:07:41,020 --> 00:07:42,650
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Quiero a mamá!</font>

87
00:07:44,280 --> 00:07:48,950
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Si mamá llora, quiero abrazarla.</i></font>

88
00:07:49,660 --> 00:07:50,990
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Estar a su lado.</font>

89
00:07:52,030 --> 00:07:55,610
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡No puedo olvidarlas!</font>

90
00:08:00,170 --> 00:08:01,370
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Qué triste.</font>

91
00:08:10,260 --> 00:08:11,350
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Estamos rodeados.</font>

92
00:08:11,930 --> 00:08:13,910
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Miorine! ¡Chicos!</font>

93
00:08:14,390 --> 00:08:16,670
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Si no entras en razón,</font>

94
00:08:17,810 --> 00:08:19,140
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">yo tampoco dudaré.</font>

95
00:08:20,400 --> 00:08:21,370
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Ericht!</font>

96
00:08:28,110 --> 00:08:30,870
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Por favor, detente, Ericht!</font>

97
00:08:50,300 --> 00:08:51,570
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Los Mobile Suits…</font>

98
00:08:52,140 --> 00:08:53,630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¿Se detuvieron?</font>

99
00:08:54,300 --> 00:08:55,690
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¿Qué ocurrió?</font>

100
00:08:56,060 --> 00:08:57,390
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Chuchu! ¡Nika!</font>

101
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:58,730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Sí!</font>

102
00:09:01,520 --> 00:09:04,210
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¿Por qué sigues molestando?</font>

103
00:09:04,730 --> 00:09:07,110
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡La tormenta cumplirá nuestro deseo!</font>

104
00:09:10,620 --> 00:09:11,800
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¿Cuál es la causa?</font>

105
00:09:12,240 --> 00:09:14,150
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Hay una intervención de datos.</i></font>

106
00:09:14,780 --> 00:09:17,190
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Disminuye a densidad de información.</i></font>

107
00:09:18,120 --> 00:09:19,200
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¿Adónde va?</font>

108
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:24,730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">A eliminar una plaga.</font>

109
00:09:25,880 --> 00:09:30,570
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Capitana, tenemos una llamada oculta
de la sede de la Unión.</font>

110
00:09:32,340 --> 00:09:37,490
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Lagrange 1 tiene un sistema
de transmisión láser interplanetaria.</font>

111
00:09:37,930 --> 00:09:39,980
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Me gustaría usarlo.</font>

112
00:09:40,640 --> 00:09:43,370
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>¿Y la reunión que solicitó Delling?</i></font>

113
00:09:44,060 --> 00:09:46,930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>No aceptamos sus condiciones.</i></font>

114
00:09:48,230 --> 00:09:54,090
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">El sistema láser es una tapadera para
desarrollar un arma interplanetaria.</font>

115
00:09:55,030 --> 00:09:59,510
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Y así parece que esta vez
se activó por error.</font>

116
00:09:59,870 --> 00:10:01,150
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Si se usa,</font>

117
00:10:01,410 --> 00:10:05,310
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">toda la zona de Lagrange 4
recibirá daños, no solo Benerit.</font>

118
00:10:05,710 --> 00:10:09,990
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">-¿Quién asumirá la responsabilidad?
<i>-Nosotros, obviamente.</i></font>

119
00:10:11,340 --> 00:10:13,790
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Tras el error de la Unión,</font>

120
00:10:14,050 --> 00:10:18,510
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">los gobiernos y empresas
autónomos de Lagrange 1</font>

121
00:10:18,680 --> 00:10:21,610
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">encabezarán la reconstrucción.</font>

122
00:10:22,020 --> 00:10:26,710
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Nuestra empresa supervisará
el grupo tras la mediación.</font>

123
00:10:27,190 --> 00:10:29,870
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Se nos prometió.</font>

124
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:46,190
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Vamos. Síganme.</font>

125
00:10:48,750 --> 00:10:51,550
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Aquí dentro, la tormenta se sobrelleva.</font>

126
00:10:51,800 --> 00:10:53,470
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Qué alivio.</font>

127
00:10:58,220 --> 00:10:59,230
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Toma.</font>

128
00:11:00,100 --> 00:11:02,090
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Estás entrenada, ¿no?</font>

129
00:11:02,390 --> 00:11:03,930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">No puedo…</font>

130
00:11:04,310 --> 00:11:06,630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">No se la daré a un estudiante.</font>

131
00:11:09,400 --> 00:11:12,550
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Usemos los códigos de detención
de una vez.</font>

132
00:11:12,780 --> 00:11:14,850
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Espera, Chuchu!</font>

133
00:11:18,660 --> 00:11:21,530
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">-¿Un Haro?
-Los intrusos serán eliminados.</font>

134
00:11:29,840 --> 00:11:33,030
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¿Así son los Gundams?</font>

135
00:11:34,300 --> 00:11:37,130
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Con esto puedo estar
a la altura de Guel.</font>

136
00:11:38,470 --> 00:11:40,430
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Podré detenerlo!</font>

137
00:11:41,050 --> 00:11:44,590
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Y eliminar a la bruja. A Miorine.</font>

138
00:11:45,020 --> 00:11:48,730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Suficiente, Lauda! ¡No sigas!</font>

139
00:11:49,060 --> 00:11:50,690
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Abre los ojos, hermano!</font>

140
00:11:58,490 --> 00:12:00,610
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">La muerte de papá.</font>

141
00:12:01,320 --> 00:12:03,390
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">El daño que sufrió Petra.</font>

142
00:12:03,910 --> 00:12:07,280
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Si no la harás pagar por ello…</font>

143
00:12:07,500 --> 00:12:09,370
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡No! ¡Escúchame, Lauda!</font>

144
00:12:09,620 --> 00:12:12,690
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>¡Yo defenderé el orgullo de los Jeturk!</i></font>

145
00:12:14,800 --> 00:12:17,970
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">A ti te confundió esa bruja,</font>

146
00:12:18,340 --> 00:12:21,390
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">así que cargaré con tus pecados.</font>

147
00:12:21,800 --> 00:12:25,270
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Yo, Lauda Jeturk!</font>

148
00:12:37,690 --> 00:12:39,390
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¿Tú eres Lauda?</font>

149
00:12:50,290 --> 00:12:51,430
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Soy Guel.</font>

150
00:12:51,710 --> 00:12:55,250
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Me alegra mucho tener
un hermano pequeño.</font>

151
00:13:06,310 --> 00:13:07,390
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Gu…</font>

152
00:13:09,230 --> 00:13:11,010
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Tienes razón.</font>

153
00:13:11,940 --> 00:13:13,060
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Lo de papá…</font>

154
00:13:14,980 --> 00:13:16,290
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Y todo lo demás.</font>

155
00:13:17,110 --> 00:13:21,550
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Si tú no me lo perdonas…</font>

156
00:13:24,830 --> 00:13:27,070
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Corre, Guel.</font>

157
00:13:27,490 --> 00:13:30,250
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">No huiré más.</font>

158
00:13:30,960 --> 00:13:33,630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Ni de papá ni de ti.</i></font>

159
00:13:35,000 --> 00:13:36,010
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Así que…</font>

160
00:13:38,550 --> 00:13:41,610
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">no pilotees de nuevo un Gundam.</font>

161
00:13:44,930 --> 00:13:47,370
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Lo siento, Guel.</font>

162
00:13:50,020 --> 00:13:51,170
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Lo siento.</font>

163
00:13:56,820 --> 00:13:58,720
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¿Son idiotas o qué les pasa?</font>

164
00:13:58,980 --> 00:13:59,950
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¿Felsi?</font>

165
00:14:00,150 --> 00:14:04,280
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Morir en una pelea entre hermanos
es estúpido!</font>

166
00:14:08,910 --> 00:14:10,200
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Tienes razón.</font>

167
00:14:11,790 --> 00:14:14,850
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Es completamente estúpido.</font>

168
00:14:19,710 --> 00:14:21,300
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Agáchate, idiota!</font>

169
00:14:21,760 --> 00:14:23,250
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¿De dónde la sacaste?</font>

170
00:14:23,550 --> 00:14:24,930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¿Qué importa eso?</font>

171
00:14:26,010 --> 00:14:28,540
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Winston, ve al bloque central
con Miorine.</font>

172
00:14:28,760 --> 00:14:29,510
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Pero…</font>

173
00:14:29,930 --> 00:14:30,870
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Ve, Miorine!</font>

174
00:14:31,100 --> 00:14:32,590
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Acaba con esto!</font>

175
00:14:32,770 --> 00:14:34,570
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Háganlo lo más rápido posible.</font>

176
00:14:43,070 --> 00:14:44,110
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">En marcha.</font>

177
00:14:45,110 --> 00:14:46,450
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yo me encargo.</font>

178
00:14:46,700 --> 00:14:48,450
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Esta vez no matarán a nadie.</font>

179
00:14:49,910 --> 00:14:52,150
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Hablas mucho.</font>

180
00:15:00,170 --> 00:15:01,130
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Es aquí.</font>

181
00:15:07,890 --> 00:15:09,730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Detenlo de una buena vez.</font>

182
00:15:10,010 --> 00:15:10,990
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Ya lo sé!</font>

183
00:15:14,140 --> 00:15:15,060
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Déjame.</font>

184
00:15:17,560 --> 00:15:18,690
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¿Por qué…?</font>

185
00:15:19,270 --> 00:15:23,400
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Cambié los códigos
de detención de emergencia.</font>

186
00:15:24,150 --> 00:15:26,310
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¿Creíste que no lo sabía?</font>

187
00:15:31,030 --> 00:15:33,370
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Miorine está con mamá.</font>

188
00:15:35,290 --> 00:15:38,810
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Si es para ganar una cosa, mamá…</font>

189
00:15:39,250 --> 00:15:40,390
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡No!</font>

190
00:15:40,790 --> 00:15:45,010
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Pues no nos robes el hogar
a mamá y a mí.</font>

191
00:15:48,090 --> 00:15:50,470
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Detén esto!</font>

192
00:15:50,930 --> 00:15:51,930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¿Por qué?</font>

193
00:15:52,390 --> 00:15:55,770
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Eri fue bendecida
por los ideales de Vanadis.</font>

194
00:15:56,730 --> 00:15:59,810
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Pero no hay lugar para ella
en este mundo.</font>

195
00:16:00,610 --> 00:16:02,270
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Por eso debemos creárselo.</font>

196
00:16:03,270 --> 00:16:05,850
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Un lugar en el que pueda ser feliz.</font>

197
00:16:07,320 --> 00:16:11,160
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Siempre hablas de Eri…
¿Y no importa qué le suceda a Suletta?</font>

198
00:16:11,320 --> 00:16:12,670
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">La amo.</font>

199
00:16:13,240 --> 00:16:15,580
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Pero ella los tiene a ustedes, ¿no?</font>

200
00:16:17,160 --> 00:16:20,290
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¿Sabes por qué subió al Calibarn?</font>

201
00:16:22,290 --> 00:16:24,450
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Temblaba porque podría morir.</font>

202
00:16:25,050 --> 00:16:28,670
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Pero lo ignoró porque las quiere.</font>

203
00:16:29,340 --> 00:16:30,870
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Porque las ama!</font>

204
00:16:32,220 --> 00:16:35,600
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Si eres su madre, ¡ámala igual!</font>

205
00:16:37,640 --> 00:16:39,050
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Eres muy crítica.</font>

206
00:16:43,360 --> 00:16:45,570
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¿Acaso revisarás el programa?</font>

207
00:16:45,710 --> 00:16:48,100
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Si evito
los privilegios de administrador…</font>

208
00:16:54,660 --> 00:16:57,250
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Entréguenme la uni…</font>

209
00:17:00,250 --> 00:17:05,000
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Ya no puedo seguir huyendo.</font>

210
00:17:17,310 --> 00:17:18,640
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Date prisa!</font>

211
00:17:18,810 --> 00:17:20,830
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Cállate! ¡Ya lo sé!</font>

212
00:17:29,570 --> 00:17:33,770
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">En el código genético
había una especie de mensaje.</font>

213
00:17:33,980 --> 00:17:36,910
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Al transformarlo en letras,
aparecieron palabras.</font>

214
00:17:41,290 --> 00:17:42,450
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">"Yo también…</font>

215
00:17:44,170 --> 00:17:45,170
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">te amo".</font>

216
00:17:50,840 --> 00:17:53,340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Todo sea por mi amada hija.</font>

217
00:17:54,890 --> 00:17:57,650
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Las madres somos muy fuertes, señorita.</font>

218
00:18:04,310 --> 00:18:05,310
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Mamá!</font>

219
00:18:21,870 --> 00:18:23,160
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Tenemos conexión.</font>

220
00:18:23,330 --> 00:18:25,330
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Enlace Permet confirmado.</font>

221
00:18:25,920 --> 00:18:27,730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Inicien el llamamiento.</font>

222
00:18:28,040 --> 00:18:31,490
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Recibido.
Entrando en el sistema de Quiet Zero.</font>

223
00:18:40,930 --> 00:18:41,930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Mamá!</font>

224
00:18:42,100 --> 00:18:43,990
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Úsenlo todo en seguridad.</font>

225
00:18:44,140 --> 00:18:45,820
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">No podemos seguir el ritmo.</font>

226
00:19:09,670 --> 00:19:10,800
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¿Se detuvo?</font>

227
00:19:11,380 --> 00:19:13,630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">La tormenta desapareció.</font>

228
00:19:14,130 --> 00:19:15,950
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Estamos bien!</font>

229
00:19:16,970 --> 00:19:18,970
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Genial!</font>

230
00:19:19,350 --> 00:19:21,150
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Misión cumplida!</font>

231
00:19:25,270 --> 00:19:27,100
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">No eres una buena asesina.</font>

232
00:19:27,730 --> 00:19:29,980
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Mejor dedícate a salvar a alguien.</font>

233
00:19:32,730 --> 00:19:34,610
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Si avanzas, ganas dos.</font>

234
00:19:35,240 --> 00:19:36,830
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Lo decías tú, ¿no?</font>

235
00:19:37,450 --> 00:19:39,630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Pues aprende de ello y avanza.</font>

236
00:19:40,700 --> 00:19:43,790
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Suletta, Ericht y tú.</font>

237
00:19:44,290 --> 00:19:47,670
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Porque seremos familia.</font>

238
00:19:49,920 --> 00:19:53,000
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Quiet Zero se detuvo.</i></font>

239
00:19:53,880 --> 00:19:56,030
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Retírense, por favor.</i></font>

240
00:19:56,880 --> 00:19:58,010
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>No.</i></font>

241
00:19:58,840 --> 00:20:04,190
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Sus empresas
se volvieron demasiado grandes.</font>

242
00:20:06,810 --> 00:20:09,440
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Preparativos de transmisión en fase 5.</font>

243
00:20:09,760 --> 00:20:12,270
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Matriz establecida
en parámetros aceptables.</font>

244
00:20:12,650 --> 00:20:15,110
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Sistema de control de fase correcto.</font>

245
00:20:16,610 --> 00:20:19,510
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Previsión de trayectoria finalizada.</font>

246
00:20:24,830 --> 00:20:27,310
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Iniciando
prueba de rayo de alta potencia</font>

247
00:20:27,500 --> 00:20:30,530
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">del sistema de transmisión láser
interplanetaria.</font>

248
00:20:39,840 --> 00:20:40,830
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡No!</font>

249
00:20:50,480 --> 00:20:52,450
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡No, Eri!</font>

250
00:21:53,000 --> 00:21:54,170
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¿Hola?</font>

251
00:22:08,010 --> 00:22:09,330
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">¡Eri!</font>

